description:
This is a 22 minute workout called 'Face Your Fears Row' from the channel Aisyah Rafaee.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Embrace your fears and have confidence in yourself as Aisyah leads you through intervals climbing in rhythm. 

Max rhythm: 30, Format: Interval ...
